00:18:03.630 --> 00:18:08.320
If there are other ways to perform that
same technology that is in the patent,

00:18:08.530 --> 00:18:09.880
it is not essential.

00:18:09.980 --> 00:18:11.990
It's as simple as that.

00:18:12.340 --> 00:18:16.320
