00:22:20.500 --> 00:22:25.160
So it was a very significant thing to
reduce the royalty and increase the

00:22:25.450 --> 00:22:27.770
compliance by many market sectors.

00:22:27.770 --> 00:22:30.980
And in this age of convergence,
that is no small thing.

00:22:31.020 --> 00:22:34.940
I'm sure you all realize,
