00:27:21.340 --> 00:27:25.180
this is a voluntary exercise
for the benefit of the market.

00:27:25.480 --> 00:27:26.860
It's a way of marketing the technology.

00:27:26.860 --> 00:27:28.520
It's a way of marketing the patents.

00:27:28.560 --> 00:27:33.070
It's a way of providing a service to
users who want to use the technology.

00:27:33.760 --> 00:27:37.370
