to the drawing board,

00:29:03.910 --> 00:29:08.480
we thought it made more sense to
include all of the profiles in part two.

00:29:08.500 --> 00:29:11.540
We didn't want to set up a
situation where a user starts to

00:29:11.610 --> 00:29:16.620
