00:31:47.700 --> 00:31:50.290
name shows up on this license,

00:31:50.390 --> 00:31:55.010
If they have an essential patent in
another country other than what's listed,

00:31:55.040 --> 00:31:57.670
or those that are listed,
that eventually they're

00:31:57.720 --> 00:31:59.190
going to be included.

00:31:59.930 --> 00:32:01.850
That they can't come
later and say to you,

00:32:01.920 --> 00:32:04.660
